Description:
Designer Inspired Delight
Simply move in, relax and enjoy the spoils this meticulously renovated three bedroom, two bathroom single level family residence has to offer. Delivering a safe, harmonious environment, the property boasts sundrenched alfresco entertaining areas and private landscaped gardens unfolding from impeccably presented open plan meals, designer inspired kitchen and generous living zone/home theatre, complete with projector/screen and surround sound system. Showcasing AEG cook top, stainless steel wall oven, dishwasher, stone benches and soft-close cabinetry, the kitchen is certain to leave a lasting impression. There are three beautifully appointed bedrooms, two have built-in-robes, including main flaunting a modern ensuite. Quality finishes are displayed throughout an immaculate family bathroom and modern laundry. While ducted heating, split-system, ceiling fans, double-glazing, plantation shutters, alarm/cameras, cute cubby house, workshop/storage and excellent off street parking, comprising tandem carport/garage with remote control entry, add appeal. In a quiet residential pocket it is close to Keilor Village, Keilor Central Shopping Centre, schools, parklands, buses and freeways.

Description:
Fulfil Your Keilor Dream
Advance your portfolio with this promising three bedroom home situated in one of Keilor's most sought-after and family friendly neighbourhoods. Offering land size of 535m2 (approx.) and located in an elite position close to Keilor Village shops, public transport, parks, prestige schools and freeway access; this rare renovator includes dual side driveway access on level land. A comfortable wraparound living room adjoins the kitchen/dining area fitted with timber cabinetry/drawers, tiled splashback, 600mm oven/grill and 900mm 4 burner gas cooktop. A sizeable central bathroom includes a separate shower and spa bath. Extras include a garage with workshop/storage facility, Rinnai heating and reverse cycle air conditioning. Description:
Upscaled Living In The Esteemed Calder Rise Estate
Presenting expansive family living with this light filled six bedroom, three bathroom home enviably located close to Overnewton College, St Augustine's Primary School, Keilor Village shops, public transport and easy freeway access. Landscaped gardens frame the property, with glorious raked ceilings heightening the sense of space within; unique to the character of this free flowing residence. Encompassing formal lounge with brick fireplace, formal dining and family room. As a central hub, the huge kitchen/meals with breakfast bar features stainless steel appliances, timber cabinetry/drawers, and tiled splashback. A privately situated alfresco entertaining area overlooks a refreshing solar-heated salt chlorinated pool, with a cute kids cubby house beyond. Accommodation is split over two levels with the three upstairs bedrooms complemented by a retreat area infused with natural light. All bathrooms are well appointed with shower facilities. Extras include WIR/BIRs, remote controlled drive-through garage, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, air conditioner, fans, solar panels, extensive storage, external awnings, garden shed.

Description:
A designer family paradise
A magnificent statement in luxury family living. Architect-designed and lavished with designer features throughout, boasting fabulous views across Keilor village.
This outstanding family residence delivers a stunning split-level floor plan of some 63 squares (approx.) featuring elegant formal and informal living and dining areas; a fully equipped home theatre, a beautiful ultra-modern kitchen with state-of-the-art gas cooking, granite benchtops and butler’s pantry; a family room opening out to a very large alfresco entertaining area which overlooks a beautiful, inviting solar-heated swimming pool.
Accommodation upstairs is provided via two complete master suites one with its own private balcony overlooking the village, three more fully-robed bedrooms and a luxury family bathroom. In addition, on the ground floor, there is a fully self-contained living zone with separate kitchen and living area overlooking the pool, two bedrooms and a bathroom.
This extraordinary residence benefits from luxury features including double remote garage, zoned ducted heating and cooling, ducted vacuum system, alarm security, and double-glazed windows throughout. The location is superb with beautiful parks and the Maribyrnong River just around the corner, it's moments’ walk from Keilor village and it's only 25 minutes to the CBD.

Description:
Beautiful Family Home Or Solid Investment
Situated in a premium Keilor locale, this gorgeous three bedroom, two bathroom home encompasses idyllic family living at its finest. Polished timber floorboards, plantation shutters, timber venetians and high ceilings set the scene with meticulous attention to detail throughout. Wrap-around lounge/dining connects to smart galley style kitchen/meals with soft-close cabinetry, walk-in-pantry and stainless steel appliances. Entertaining continues outside with a fabulous timber decked pergola, sunny paved courtyard and gazebo with inbuilt natural gas BBQ and impressive polished concrete benchtop, a perfect space for lazy Sunday afternoons. The bedrooms all boast large proportions and include built-in-robes, while a contemporary, fully tiled ensuite featuring trendy white subway tiles and charcoal flooring provide a touch of luxury for the impressive master. The central bathroom reflects this contemporary theme with shower, bath and wave feature vanity. Includes garage with additional OSP, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, ceiling fans, water tank. Close to Keilor Village, schools including Overnewton, parks, transport and easy freeway access.

Description:
Family Haven Enjoys Botanical Bliss
Lavished with space, style and a glorious botanical setting, this impeccably renovated four bedroom, three bathroom family residence offers all the versatility that growing household's demand. Set on approximately 1101m2, at the end of a coveted court, the home's alluring interiors comprise sophisticated living room, featuring gas log fire, elegant dining room and vast open plan kitchen, meals, family zones large enough to easily cater for social festivities and day-to-day living. Spilling from a delightful sitting room, highlighted by floor-to-ceiling glass aspects with electric blinds, are sundrenched deck, spectacular north-facing gardens and an expansive, all-weather alfresco entertaining zone complemented by gas-to-mains barbeque. A hostess kitchen showcases stone island/counters, 900mm stainless steel gas cook top, electric wall ovens, double-drawer dishwasher and bountiful storage options. Great accommodation is provided by four beautiful bedrooms, including main with walk-in-robe and ensuite. Features BIRS, pristine bathrooms, ducted heating/evaporative cooling, large workshop/shed, automated double garage and more. Close to quality schools, Watergardens, buses, freeways and airports.

Description:
A Family Delight In The Perfect Locale
Solidly built and flaunting a versatile floor plan with easy enhancement potential, this two storey three bedroom plus study, two bathroom home will delight market entrants and growing families. This well loved residence comprises a broad living and dining room with an enclosed retro bar, split system and soaring ceilings which enhance the space. Situated to the rear of the home is an open plan kitchen and family room showcasing updated stainless steel appliances including dishwasher plus generous bench space and cabinetry. Glass sliders reveal a spacious paved alfresco, while enveloping the home is an easy care garden including a mature lemon tree and garden shed. The master bedroom resides on the ground floor enjoying original ensuite and dual floor to ceiling BIR's while atop the timber staircase is two additional bedrooms serviced by a central bathroom and private W/C. Further highlights include double carport, ducted heating, hardwood floors throughout and a second toilet via the spacious laundry. Bus service, Keilor Village, excellent schools including Overnewton College and St Augustines are all mere minutes away as is Brimbank Park, Watergardens shopping centre, train station and freeway access.
